<resources>
    <string name="llm_tool_schedule_import_from_icalendar_description">Get the method for importing semesters, courses, and events from iCalendar data, supporting recurring events. This method is preferred when there are a large number of recurring events in the schedule or when creating a course schedule; it is recommended to obtain it together with `create_semester`.</string>
    <string name="llm_tool_schedule_import_from_icalendar_creation_rule">"
        Method for creating iCalendar content

        - You need to put the iCalendar content in a Markdown Code Fence;
        - The language tag of the Code Fence must be set to `%1$s`;
        - If you correctly use the Code Fence as required to provide the iCalendar content, the user will see an import button, and if the user clicks that button, you will receive the result of this import.
    "</string>

